WEBVTT

00:00:29.941 --> 00:00:32.469
umetengenezwa na kipande kimoja cha
sanamu.

00:00:32.845 --> 00:00:34.438
Hakuna saa.

00:00:34.462 --> 00:00:36.002
Hakuna kamba,

00:00:36.026 --> 00:00:37.456
na hakuna karatasi.

00:00:38.022 --> 00:00:41.805
Ni kipande kimoja cha mkangazi wa
Honduras uliong'arishwa.

00:00:42.969 --> 00:00:44.659
Sasa ngoja nieleze kwa ufasaha:

00:00:44.683 --> 00:00:49.201
zoezi hili halikuwa kuhusu
kuangalia sanamu.

00:00:50.509 --> 00:00:51.659
Ni kuhusu kutazama

00:00:52.440 --> 00:00:57.215
na kuelewa kwamba kuangalia kwa
ukaribu huokoa maisha,

00:00:57.239 --> 00:00:58.709
kubadili kampuni yako

00:00:58.733 --> 00:01:02.996
na hata kuelewa kwanini watoto
wako wanafanya tabia fulani.